# Keep the build context lean but DO NOT deny-all: the Vite build needs
# index.html, vite.config.ts, tsconfig*.json, src/, excalidraw-app/, public/,
# scripts/, .env.* — so we only exclude heavy/irrelevant paths here.
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
build
dist
coverage
*.log
firebase-project
dev-docs
.codesandbox
